1. *Zadnjem* redu su ostala samo dva slobodna mesta. (In the *last* row, there are only two free seats left.)
2. Pokupio sam *zadnjem* brzinom stvari koje su mi bile potrebne. (I gathered the things I needed in the *fastest* possible time.)
3. Vozač je rekao da će nas *zadnjem* delu autobusa biti previše gužve. (The driver said that there would be too much crowding in the *back* of the bus.)
4. Došao je u *zadnjem* trenutku i sprečio nezgodu. (He came at the *last* moment and prevented an accident.)
5. Ukoliko budeš radio ovaj zadatak, proći ćeš *zadnjem* testiranju. (If you complete this task, you will pass the *final* test.)
6. Čekaću te na *zadnjem* peronu železničke stanice. (I'll wait for you at the *last* platform of the railway station.)
7. Moramo proveriti da li su vrata na *zadnjem* ulazu zaključana. (We need to check if the door at the *rear* entrance is locked.)
8. *Zadnjem* putu sam te rekao da ne dolaziš kući kasno. (The *last* time, I told you not to come home late.)

Note: The word "zadnjem" can be translated into English as "last," "fastest," "back," "final," "rear," etc., depending on the context in which it is used.